"eventually failures."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2020-11-02-quarkus-native-on-a-raspberry-pi.adoc:85
msgid ""
"The reason why Podman is the contained of choice is very well explained in "
"the following "
"https://podman.io/blogs/2019/10/29/podman-crun-f31.html[article].  I'm "
"quoting the quick explanation:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Positional ($2) AttributeList argument for style 'quote'
#: upstream/_posts/2020-11-02-quarkus-native-on-a-raspberry-pi.adoc:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "Rūmī"
