#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2020-11-02-quarkus-native-on-a-raspberry-pi.adoc:281
msgid ""
"After the flashing operation has completed successfully, it's important to "
"have a look at the config file of the operating system. edit the file "
"_config.txt_ and make sure the section *[all]* starts with the following "
"key-value pairs: arm_control=0x200, arm_64bit=1"
